(Everything reflects the darkness)

405
00:22:09,398 --> 00:22:11,945
(When it's inside of my hand)

406
00:22:11,970 --> 00:22:14,708
(Everything reflects the darkness)

407
00:22:15,879 --> 00:22:18,304
(Shadow is the light)

408
00:22:18,364 --> 00:22:21,247
(背負著沉重命運)

409
00:22:21,272 --> 00:22:26,093
(隨著那一次次染血記憶)

410
00:22:26,093 --> 00:22:31,136
(刺穿那些黑暗的影子吧)

411
00:22:31,527 --> 00:22:36,228
(用漆黑的雙手破壞一切)

412
00:22:36,253 --> 00:22:37,561
(I'll never change)

413
00:22:37,561 --> 00:22:39,966
(Everything reflects the darkness)

414
00:22:39,966 --> 00:22:42,562
(When it's inside of my hand)

415
00:22:42,587 --> 00:22:47,697
(Everything reflects the darkness)

416
00:23:08,680 --> 00:23:10,445
放棄無謂的抵抗吧

417
00:23:28,967 --> 00:23:31,146
他就在這裡吧

418
00:23:34,969 --> 00:23:37,081
(下一回)

419
00:23:37,106 --> 00:30:24,702
(死靈術師)

